{"id": 5515, "title": "Ticket #5515: Add SLURM support via the blahp", "description": "<blockquote>\nTo submit jobs to SLURM, we currently rely on an optional PBS-emulation module of SLURM. We'd prefer to use SLURM's native interface. Installation of the PBS-emulation module may not be possible, and the native interface gives us access to more options. Also, it's less confusing to the user.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5742\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5742'); return false;\" title=\"Blahp slurm file leak\">#5742</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nBlahp slurm file leak</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5780\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5780'); return false;\" title=\"Allow specifying SLURM partition\">#5780</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAllow specifying SLURM partition</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=5804\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5804'); return false;\" title=\"Syntax error in slurm_cancel.sh\">#5804</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nSyntax error in slurm_cancel.sh</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr